{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "李坏酒醉醒来，发现落入大内总捕头韩峻手中。韩峻一反常态，以冷漠而非严厉的态度审问他是否盗窃大内银库一百七十万两库银。黑暗中另有一神秘人（后揭晓为徐青石），以温和威严的声音鼓励李坏如实交代。李坏坦白了自己的身世：多年前铁银衣找到他，带他回归李家，传他飞刀小册；其母留下锦囊，内藏地图指引他找到上官金虹金钱帮遗留的宝藏，他在那里独处七年练成飞刀绝技。灯光亮起，大厅中坐着九位气度不凡的老人，为首的徐青石（字坚白，号青石）表明身份——他是李家世交，官居一品，此次出面是为李坏澄清冤屈。徐青石告知李坏，一位姓方的姑娘曾想见他最后一面却改了主意。最终，李坏被告知已完全自由，未来由自己决定。章末，李坏在风雪中回想着父亲的关切，内心深受触动。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_jun",
      "speaker_name": "韩峻",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你是不是姓李，是不是叫李坏？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_han_jun",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_jun",
      "speaker_name": "韩峻",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "大内银库所失窃的那一百七十万两库银，是不是你盗去的？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_han_jun",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_jun",
      "speaker_name": "韩峻",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你的意思是说，你和内库的那件盗案完全没有关系？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_han_jun",
      "text": "是的，我和那件案子完全无关。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_jun",
      "speaker_name": "韩峻",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "那么你这几个月来所挥霍花去的钱财，是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_han_jun",
      "text": "我的钱财是从哪里来的，好像也跟你没有关系，连一点狗屁的关系都没有。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中的人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "李坏，没有关系的。不管韩总捕问你什么，你都不妨大胆照实说。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中的人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "只要你说的是实话，我们一定会给你一个公道。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中的人",
      "listener": "char_han_jun",
      "text": "韩总捕，你再问。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中的人",
      "listener": "char_han_jun",
      "text": "我相信他不会不说实话的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这是你父亲要我交给你的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这些日子来，我相信你父亲教给你很多关于飞刀的秘法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "再加上这个册子里的要诀和你自己的苦练，我相信你一定可以练成你们李家的飞刀，因为你本来就是李家的人，你的血里面本来就有你们李家的血。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这个锦囊里有什么？就没有人知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为这个锦囊是你母亲要你父亲交给你的，我们谁也没有打开来看过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你所找到的那一宗宝藏，价值究竟有多大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "text": "我相信，它的价值绝不会在大内失窃的库银之下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我相信你说的是真话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "text": "我说的每一个字都是真话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "那么我就不得不问你一件事了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你的母亲是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "text": "先母复姓上官。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "难道令堂就是上官小仙？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "text": "不是。仙姨是先母之姐，先母是她的妹妹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "难道你所找到的那一宗宝藏，就是昔年上官金虹的金钱帮遗留在人间的宝藏？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我知道你从来没有见过我，可是我相信你一定知道我的名字。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我姓徐，字坚白，号青石。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我们这次出面，都是为了你来澄清这件事的，因为我们都是令尊的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "令尊相信你绝不是一个会为了钱财而去犯罪的人，我们也相信他的看法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "所以我们这些久已不问世事的老头子，这次才会挺身而出。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "现在事情的真相终于已水落石出，现在我只希望你明白，一个做父亲的人，对儿子的关切，永远不是做儿子的所能了解的。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你实在应该以能够做你父亲的儿子为荣。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "还有一件事，我要告诉你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "有一位姓方的姑娘，本来想见你最后一面的，我也答应了她，可是后来她自己又改变了主意。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "现在，你在我们这一方面的事情已经全部了结了。对我们来说，你已经是个完全自由的人了。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "徐青石",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "以后你应该怎么做，想去做些什么事，都完全由你自己来决定。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    }
  ],
